descriptionNullable:
This database is composed of  : 
- 10 images, Each image contains 624 samples for one digit from 0 to 9 ( the description is  in the provenance section).
- One matlab program  to localised ( extracted) each digit in the image

This database is used in the classification framework by a doctoral study, here is the link of the thesis : 
   http://eprints.univ-batna2.dz/1905/
